Requirements
============

- ZF2 library (https://github.com/zendframework/zf2.git)
  Install or symlink the library/Zend/ directory to library/Zend/.
- Fig library (https://github.com/weierophinney/fig-library.git)
  Use the "zf-implementation" branch.
  Install or symlink the library/Fig/ directory to library/Fig/.
